metadata.name: STOP
metadata.description:
A fairy tale love gone to waste,
as life grew a sickly bitter taste.
Some mindless words guided me,
like the forgotten memories from antiquity.
Calling me with a whisper, a touch, a plea.
I'd have come if it was as it used to be.

Zamanlar icinde,
Gercek bir askti...
Yasamin icinden,
Aci bir tatti..
Kimi olmus sacma sozler,
Eskilerden unutulmus yadigardi.

Bir fisiltiyla, bir yakarisla, bir dokunusla,
Cagiriyorsan eger...
Gelirdim, eskiden olsaydi....

Song and Lyrics written by LolaRheaStyx

special thanks to Motomot production for the help with arranging the song.


high res video available upon request.
